  "profile": {
    "summary": "Carlos Mendoza is a 39-year-old Mexican executive chef and co-owner of 'Raíz', a modern Mexican restaurant in Mexico City. He is married to Valentina, a pastry chef, and they have two children, Diego (8) and Sofia (5). Carlos is a culinary innovator, specializing in reimagining pre-Hispanic ingredients for contemporary cuisine, and has received recognition in Mexican food publications. Outside of his professional life, he coaches youth football, collects vintage mezcal, and maintains a rooftop herb garden.",
